text: Hu he adwæscte þæt gedwimorlice fyr.
Hu he gehælde þone cnapan, þe wæs mid hryre tocwysed.
Hu þa gebroðra æton & druncan buton leafe.
Be Ualentinianes breðer.
Hu he arasode þa hiwunge Totillan cininge.
Be þære witegunge, þe wæs geworden be þam ylcan cininge Totillan.
Hu he alysde þone preost fram deofle.
Hu he witegode be his mynstres toworpennysse.
Hu he þurh gast wiste þa behyddan flaxan.
Hu se Godes þeow onfeng þa sceatas.
Hu he oncneow þurh gast þæs cnapan modinysse.
Hu þa twa hund mittena melewes wæron fundene æt þam mynstergeate.
Hu he þurh gesihþe gedihte þa mynstertimbrunge neah Terracine.
Hu þa Godes þeowena æfter deaðe wurdon amansumode.
Hu se eorðe awearp þone munuccnapan of his byrgenne.
Hu se munuc gemette þone dracan, þa þe he of mynstre ut gewat.
Hu he gehælde þone man fram þære micelan adle.
Hu þa scillingas wurdon þurh wundor agifene þam biddendum.
Hu þæt glæsfæt wæs aworpen uppon þa stanas & næs tobroken.
Hu seo æmtige kyf wearð mid ele gefylled.
Hu he alysde þone munuc fram deofle.
Hu he mid his eagum unband þone ceorl.
Hu he awehte þone deadan.
Be Scolastican wundre his swustor.
Hu he geseah his swustor sawle, hu heo utferde of lichaman.
Hu he geseah ealne middaneard under anum leoman & Germanes bisceopes sawle.
Hu he awrat munuca regol.
Hu he witegode þam broðrum be his forðfore.
Hu þæt wode wif wearð gehæled æt his scræfe.
Her endiað þa capitulas þære æftran boce.
